; Coverage test for history.cc L372-378, L469-482
; Tests price inversion in find_price. When the price graph has an edge
; from EUR to $ (P EUR 1.10 $), converting $ to EUR requires inverting
; the price. This exercises the inversion paths where price.commodity()
; matches the source commodity.

P 2024/01/01 EUR 1.10 $

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash     -$10.00

; Dual-target find_price with inversion (L469-482)
; $10 / 1.10 $/EUR ~ EUR 9
test bal -X EUR
               EUR-9  Assets:Cash
                EUR9  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
